snippet.title: Bake it Till' You Make it! (Early Access)
snippet.description:
https://coolboi-21.itch.io/bakingit



Bake it Till You Make it, is a cooking/sandbox releasing on the Oculus Rift Store (hopefully) sometime in March. Further details will be given toward arriving closer to the launch day. I hope you enjoy the game as I have been working on it for quite some time, and is also the first actual VR game I have made. The game is planned to be free for early access and then later paid once is actually complete. Thank you!

NOTE: AS OF 2023 THE PROJECT HAS BEEN ON HOLD, DUE TO A LACK OF TIME AND INTRESTS IN OTHER PROJECTS.

Royalty free music from https://www.FesliyanStudios.com
